From: Valentine Barshak <valentine.barshak@cogentembedded.com>
Date: Thu, 19 Mar 2015 21:53:05 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] ARM: shmobile: defconfig: Enable Bluetooth

This enables Bluetooth HCI support.

Signed-off-by: Valentine Barshak <valentine.barshak@cogentembedded.com>
---
 arch/arm/configs/shmobile_defconfig | 5 +++++
 1 file changed, 5 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm/configs/shmobile_defconfig b/arch/arm/configs/shmobile_defconfig
index 11d02ca..5f61ea8 100644
--- a/arch/arm/configs/shmobile_defconfig
+++ b/arch/arm/configs/shmobile_defconfig
@@ -74,6 +74,11 @@ CONFIG_TCP_CONG_ADVANCED=y
 CONFIG_IP_PNP=y
 CONFIG_IP_PNP_DHCP=y
 # CONFIG_IPV6 is not set
+CONFIG_BT=y
+CONFIG_BT_RFCOMM=y
+CONFIG_BT_RFCOMM_TTY=y
+CONFIG_BT_HCIUART=y
+CONFIG_BT_HCIUART_H4=y
 CONFIG_UEVENT_HELPER_PATH="/sbin/hotplug"
 CONFIG_DEVTMPFS=y
 CONFIG_DEVTMPFS_MOUNT=y
